	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: SNES-ish pixel art character: elf girl</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Looks cool. 16-bit pixel art is not my specialty, but there's a noticeable lack of volume in the face, compared to the rest of the sprite. The hair and the dress have very complex shading, so the face clashes badly with them. The proportions between the arms and the legs are a bit weird too, the legs are way too stubby compared to such long arms.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


